Class BaseTDepartment

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.apache.torque.om.BaseObject
      • com.aurel.track.persist.TpBaseObject
        • com.aurel.track.persist.BaseTDepartment
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.io.Serializable, org.apache.torque.om.Persistent
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    TDepartment

    public abstract class BaseTDepartment
extends TpBaseObject
    This table holds the departments. Each user belongs to one department. You should not use this class directly. It should not even be extended all references should be to TDepartment
